Name: Hentai Girl Run
About the game: Introduction Hentai Girl Run is a runner game,you only need to jump over the obstacles to earn money. You can get new clothes with money and unlock new levels. There is no time limit in the game and it is an endless runner game. You can relax with girl dancing with 12 different dance moves. Characteristics Can change clothes Can dance Can unlock new levels Can change hair color Cheat Mode (Left Control + Left Shift + H)
